tasks.description:
Append identity-service database variables to infra/.env.example under a labelled comment block:

# Identity Service
IDENTITY_DB_NAME=loanflow_identity_db

The shared DATABASE_HOST, DATABASE_PORT, DATABASE_USER, DATABASE_PASSWORD, and MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD variables are reused from the base MySQL block. Only the database name requires a service-specific variable.

Also update infra/mysql/init/01_init.sql to provision the identity database:
CREATE DATABASE IF NOT EXISTS loanflow_identity_db CHARACTER SET utf8mb4 COLLATE utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON loanflow_identity_db.* TO '${DATABASE_USER}'@'%';
FLUSH PRIVILEGES;
